Note on source videos:
The source videos used in VAQ-Bench are from the Video-MME benchmark
(https://video-mme.github.io/), which collects publicly available videos from
YouTube. The videos are subject to their original YouTube licenses and the
Video-MME terms of use. We do not redistribute the video files; users should
download them from the official Video-MME repository.

